First Lady Melania Trump has announced the addition of three new positions to her East Wing staff. Reagan Thompson has been hired as Director of Policy and will focus on the First Lady's policies and initiatives. Justin Caporale has accepted the position of Director of Operations and will manage the day-to-day logistical operations of the East Wing. Annie LeHardy has been hired as Communications Coordinator within the East Wing press team. The First Lady expressed excitement about the new additions and believes they will enhance her work on behalf of children and expand her role as First Lady of the United States.